      <title>欧元区债券市场模仿国债，将相关性推至创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/euro-zone-bond-markets-mimic-treasuries-pushing-correlations-record-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区债券与美国债券的交易比以往任何时候都更加同步，因为投资者忽视了欧洲经济放缓，仍然高度关注通胀和利率，推动两个市场之间的相关性在最近几周创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/euro-zone-bond-markets-mimic-treasuries-pushing-correlations-record-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 05:54:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
